WILL BE PRETTY MUCH THE SAME

325
00:20:04,708 --> 00:20:06,666
FOR ANY PASS YOU'RE ON.

326
00:20:06,750 --> 00:20:09,916
- SO WHAT DO YOU THINK?
THE KID GONNA SHOW UP TONIGHT?

327
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:11,416
- WHO THE HELL KNOWS?

328
00:20:11,500 --> 00:20:14,166
IF I WERE A BETTIN' MAN I'D SAY
THERE'S ABOUT A 40% CHANCE

329
00:20:14,250 --> 00:20:17,083
HE'S ACTUALLY GONNA SHOW HIS
FACE HERE ON THE PASS TONIGHT.

330
00:20:17,166 --> 00:20:18,791
