00:20:34,416 --> 00:20:36,958
BUT I'LL BE THE FIRST TO ADMIT
THAT I WON'T BE GETTING

338
00:20:37,041 --> 00:20:40,916
MUCH SLEEP KNOWIN' WE LET ONE
SLIP AWAY ON MOUNT AKINA.

339
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:42,541
THAT'S WHY I NEED TO
COME OUT SWINGIN'

340
00:20:42,625 --> 00:20:44,166
AND TAKE THE EIGHT-SIX DOWN NOW,

341
